column5: First day on the ice in 2021.Hope the rest of year goes as well.Went at 2 -4 seems like a good time.Lots of action and lots of fish and 2 good ones.Wayne came down with the marcum camera and we watched some muskies swimming around but have no idea how to put a video on here.iam all ears if someone knows.
That's the way to kick 'er off dood!
